Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Necron Warrior",
  "manufacturer": "Games Workshop",
  "faction": "Necrons",
  "scale": "28mm",
  "status": "unpainted"
}

### List miniatures
GET http://localhost:5000/api/miniatures
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update miniature
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/miniatures/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "primed"
}

### Delete miniature
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/miniatures/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}